data.description: Welcome to this absolutely stunning colonial home situated on over two and a half acres in Atwater.  This inviting abode offers four nicely sized bedrooms and two and a half baths.  Upon entry at the front door there is a spacious office, perfect for those that work at home.  There is a very open floor plan.  The kitchen opens to the great room that has a cozy fireplace.  The kitchen boasts oak cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious center island perfect for entertaining.  There is also a formal dining room and living room.  All of the bedrooms are situated on the second level.  The primary suite has a huge soaking tub, double bowl sinks, and amazing closet space.  Enjoy summer evenings on your screened in back deck.  The pool is perfect for hot summer days.  All of this plus a two car attached garage and a one car detached garage and a storage shed. What an amazing private lot!  Call to schedule a showing today.
